/>\n<br />\n英國唔係香港，如果政府同國民作對，輕則民望急跌下屆唔洗選，重則引發騷亂即時下台。<br />\n英國人見人話人話，見鬼講鬼話出哂名啦，除非中共一改戰狼外交方針，否則歐美政府點樣可以體面地鬆張俾你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c870953263652a42d6214b70f2805775a140074d","tid":2417671,"uid":63846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3f06f6a3fbde4f2b56485c3b646964ba3d3aa541","tid":2417671,"uid":91721,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"bd0e1de8e4233f5c42b841e3174575fedcd8a710","tid":2417671,"uid":173945,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T05:31:02.000Z","msg":"日落了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T05:34:33.000Z","msg":"日你老母<br />\n<br />\n民主國家嘅好處就係如果人民唔願意，你個首相想奶共都會俾議會阻頭阻勢，隨時呢個tenure都過唔到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T05:55:58.000Z","msg":"英國反對黨奶得仲勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff449c38afe112fd23ff94184db29f0ccd727a43","tid":2417671,"uid":91721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c870953263652a42d6214b70f2805775a140074d","tid":2417671,"uid":63846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3f06f6a3fbde4f2b56485c3b646964ba3d3aa541","tid":2417671,"uid":91721,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"bd0e1de8e4233f5c42b841e3174575fedcd8a710","tid":2417671,"uid":173945,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T05:31:02.000Z","msg":"日落了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T05:34:33.000Z","msg":"日你老母<br />\n<br />\n民主國家嘅好處就係如果人民唔願意，你個首相想奶共都會俾議會阻頭阻勢，隨時呢個tenure都過唔到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T05:55:58.000Z","msg":"英國反對黨奶得仲勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T06:02:20.000Z","msg":"而家係執政黨班議員都屌緊個首相"},{"pid":"62d654396bb48ec577de6d2198602769e7874d7f","tid":2417671,"uid":70988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff449c38afe112fd23ff94184db29f0ccd727a43","tid":2417671,"uid":91721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c870953263652a42d6214b70f2805775a140074d","tid":2417671,"uid":63846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3f06f6a3fbde4f2b56485c3b646964ba3d3aa541","tid":2417671,"uid":91721,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T05:34:33.000Z","msg":"日你老母<br />\n<br />\n民主國家嘅好處就係如果人民唔願意，你個首相想奶共都會俾議會阻頭阻勢，隨時呢個tenure都過唔到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T05:55:58.000Z","msg":"英國反對黨奶得仲勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T06:02:20.000Z","msg":"而家係執政黨班議員都屌緊個首相"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T11:07:08.000Z","msg":"英國《衛報》報道，約翰遜（Boris Johnson）本月12日於唐寧街首相府，與中資企業舉行圓桌會議。約翰遜於會議上形容自己是強烈親華派（fervently Sinophile），又指無論出現任何政治困難（whatever the occasional political difficulties），都希望加強與中國的貿易聯繫。<br />\n<br />\n約翰遜據報更於會上表示，他希望通過重啟中英年度經濟對話和中英聯合貿易和經濟委員會（JETCO），可恢復與中國的正式貿易討論。約翰遜更於圓桌會議上表明，他願意與中國簽署新投資和市場准入協議。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}